DIV1.P:
Let every one here present before the


Lord, Pray to Him to be kept and preser∣ved by Him from this & all other great Transgressions. Keep back thy servant from presumptuous sins, let them not have dominion over me: So shall I be innocent from the great Transgression. It is an ex∣cellent and needful part in our Litany;
From Envy, Hatred and Malice, and all Ʋncharitableness (& so from Mur∣der one frequent cursed Effect of them;) Good Lord deliver us.
